articles.title: Climber who died near the top of Denali, North America's tallest mountain identified - CBS News
articles.description: Zulkifli Bin Yusof, 36, was part of a three-man climbing team from Malaysia.
articles.content: A Malaysian climber likely died of exposure and altitude-related illness earlier this week after sheltering for days in a snow cave with minimal survival gear near the top of Denali, North America's … [+2171 chars]
